DLW-SPUN · the full weave of The Hoarders & the Wasters

who   : Misers and spendthrifts — many of them clergy and popes.
what  : Two mobs rolling great weights with their chests, clashing forever.
where : Circle IV — Greed (Plutus croaks above them).
why   : They loved getting and spending past all measure.
when  : Forever, at the point of collision.
how   : Faces worn featureless, pushing dead weight against the dead weight of the other side.

class : Circle IV · Greed · rolling dead weights
